name: Soo Catwoman Greetings Cards - Set Of Five
description: Say it with Soo! Did you ever notice how difficult it is to find a good greetings card? Well look no further, this set of five Soo cards is just what you need! These cards come with envelopes and are blank inside for your own message, making them perfect for any occasion. Some Soo fans have also been very creative with these cards, framing them for display purposes and using them in various art projects. We love to see what you get up to, so be sure to share your pictures on our Facebook page! Other things you might like to know: Each high quality card measures 4.13" x 5.82" Our cards are made with thick 350gsm, FSC credited paper stock. When these card sets are purchased with another item in our store, Postage & Packaging is FREE. When purchased on their own, Postage & Packaging is £1.10 to any destination worldwide.
